{
  "3310930": {
    "name": "Hue Hooligans",
    "steam_appid": 3310930,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/5e996975963f5958234ef9a4b2aff5ac.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/5e996975963f5958234ef9a4b2aff5ac.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>The goal of this game is to get all Hooligans to reach their spray indicator and tag it.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/0a6af9e3b3c65b2c6a54ff23dda30885.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/0a6af9e3b3c65b2c6a54ff23dda30885.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/a6ddb5193ccf629a44a98c6ba4627ade.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/a6ddb5193ccf629a44a98c6ba4627ade.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/968bd43312b5e30af339a657fb784842.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=139 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/968bd43312b5e30af339a657fb784842.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Each Hooligan has their own color and ability.</strong> They need to work together in order for all of them to reach their targets.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >All colors are adjustable in settings. If you have trouble differentiating them, you can change them to your liking.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/77461e2b3d249c52809efc24259cad29.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/77461e2b3d249c52809efc24259cad29.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>You take control of other Hooligans by calling them on the phone.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You may hang up whenever you want, and call them as many times as you need. Phone booths are carefully positioned on each level to make complex puzzles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/f27ed94faccee35a052d4b5dccee131c.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=519 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/f27ed94faccee35a052d4b5dccee131c.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/d481953fe8ec4fe0088910f8ecb78717.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/d481953fe8ec4fe0088910f8ecb78717.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>The main obstacles are doors</strong>, which are controlled by either buttons, levers, or pressure plates.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/c3ada6709134180d16481058f7d60cba.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=485 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/c3ada6709134180d16481058f7d60cba.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/5b2ab038ee1d40d8ee8b05db8375047c.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/5b2ab038ee1d40d8ee8b05db8375047c.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><strong>If you’re stuck on a level, you can move on. </strong>Most levels are skippable. Maybe a solution lies somewhere else?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/5e3041ac74a178cdf5ea3cf5f151c10c.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/5e3041ac74a178cdf5ea3cf5f151c10c.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/8c6888ae4fea0f9ad4f8add3ca68605c.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/8c6888ae4fea0f9ad4f8add3ca68605c.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>My goal is for each player to be satisfied and enjoy the game. With that said, this game will have a certain audience, and gamers out of that scope probably won’t enjoy it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>In any case, I encourage you to try the demo before making a purchase.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/35692c38c8826756db88c1f0daffeebf.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=139 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/35692c38c8826756db88c1f0daffeebf.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key points that will help you determine if this game is for you:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A small but challenging game with around <strong>60 puzzles</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>6+ hours</strong> of gameplay.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Special puzzles</strong> for completionists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Skippable levels</strong> – if you’re stuck, you may try another puzzle. You can always come back.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Customizable visuals</strong> (changing in-game colors and/or retro effects).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Live-action <strong>video cutscenes </strong>(not available in the Demo).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Cute characters</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hip-Hop</strong> music.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/4cb674602e773eddd894bad9af4e3aab.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/4cb674602e773eddd894bad9af4e3aab.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/0c28386adfac3acc40b2559fb24613cb.poster.avif?t=1764245796\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3310930/extras/0c28386adfac3acc40b2559fb24613cb.webm?t=1764245796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p>",
